/web/node_modules/
/web/dist/

# `make ui` copies web/dist/ here (spec smartbuster-phase5b-spec.md §2); the
# built bundle is a generated artifact, not source. PLACEHOLDER.md stays
# tracked so a bare `go build` on a fresh clone (before ever running
# `make ui`) still has a non-empty directory to embed — Go's
# `//go:embed all:assets` fails to compile against a truly empty dir.
/internal/daemon/assets/*
!/internal/daemon/assets/PLACEHOLDER.md
.claude/